    "When \"cybersecurity\" and \"dark web\" are highlighted in Figure 2, the articles likely focus on those subjects.Figure 3 gives closer glimpses of selected articles by presenting a word cloud of the mentioned keywords in articles.In the fourth stage, several criteria were used for selecting literature in this study as part of the inclusion principles focusing on dark web monitoring and business cybersecurity strategy.",
